						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the <hi rend="italic">prākāra</hi> of Durgā-Paramēśvarī temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 10th century.</p>						

						<p>This record seems to register a gift of land for a perpetual lamp in the temple of a goddess (name not clear), by Obaliabbe of Kokkaraṇi, in the kingdom of Sāntaradēva.</p>						

						<p>It is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Virōdhikṛit, Dhanus, Jupiter</hi> in <hi rend="bold">Kuṁbha.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
